---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="SoulWrap™ — JZ Stafura"
  description="A deadpan luxury wellness landing page for a fictional existential crisis solution."
>
  <div class="back"><a href="/fun/">&#x2190; Fun</a></div>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="overline">Fun / Parody</p>
    <h1>SoulWrap&#x2122;</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">An Existential Wellness Solution.</p>
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span class="status status-live">Live</span>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://jzstafura.github.io/soulwrap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit SoulWrap&#x2122; &#x2197;</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/jzstafura/soulwrap" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub &#x2197;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="preview-section">
    <a href="https://jzstafura.github.io/soulwrap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="preview-card">
      <div class="preview-inner">
        <p class="preview-tagline">&#x201C;Because the abyss gazes also, but at least it&#x2019;s cozy.&#x201D;</p>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <span>Luxury wellness aesthetic</span>
          <span>Deadpan product copy</span>
          <span>Fictional testimonials</span>
          <span>Existential comparison table</span>
          <span>CTA to philosophy archive</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="preview-cta">
        Visit SoulWrap&#x2122; &#x2197;
      </div>
    </a>
    <p class="preview-note">A parody product landing page. Opens in a new tab.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>SoulWrap&#x2122; is a single-page parody of luxury wellness brands and the broader industry of packaging existential dread as a solvable consumer problem. The aesthetic is deliberately minimal and serious &mdash; the joke works because it doesn&#x2019;t wink at you.</p>
    <p>Pure HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript. No build tools. Dedicated to the proposition that the abyss deserves better branding.</p>

    <div class="details-grid">
      <div class="detail-block">
        <h3>Stack</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Vanilla HTML / CSS / JS</li>
          <li>Smooth scrolling</li>
          <li>Responsive design</li>
          <li>No dependencies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-block">
        <h3>Disclaimer</h3>
        <p class="detail-desc">SoulWrap&#x2122; is not real and cannot actually solve existential crises. Please consult qualified mental health professionals for genuine existential concerns.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .back { padding: 1.5rem 0 0; }
  .back a { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .back a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .overline { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero { padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .hero-sub { max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; }
  .meta-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .status { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem; border: 1px solid; }
  .status-live { color: #16a34a; border-color: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.3); background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.05); }
  .links { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .links a { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: 1px; text-decoration: none; }
  .links a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .preview-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .preview-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .preview-card:hover {
    border-color: #9ca3af;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .preview-inner { padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem; }

  .preview-tagline {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-list span {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
  }

  .preview-cta {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .preview-note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 0.75rem; }

  section.about { padding-bottom: 2rem; }
  .about h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .about p { color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 65ch; }

  .details-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .detail-block h3 { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .detail-block ul { list-style: none; }
  .detail-block li { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text); padding: 0.2rem 0; }
  .detail-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; }
</style>
